  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>This hotel is on full board including wine, breakfast, lunch and dinner are taken as buffet dining. When the weather is nice, meals can be taken outside on the panoramic terrace. Meals start from dinner on the day of arrival to breakfast on the day of departure.</p>
<p>The continental buffet breakfast is served between 7.30-9.30 am.</p>
<p>Buffet style lunch is served between 12-1.30pm, and a packed lunch is available but this must be ordered the day before.</p>
<p>Three course buffet dinner is served between 7.30-8.30pm, and an early meal time of 7pm is available for children's meals. There is a weekly themed or Savoyard style meal. Christmas and New Year gala dinners are included.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
