  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Twin rooms</strong> sleep two people and are 18m². These rooms are also available for sole occupancy on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Triple rooms</strong> can sleep two adults and a child (up to 11 years old) and are 18m².</p>
<p><strong>Quad rooms</strong> can sleep four to six people and are 36m². Quad rooms are made up of two interconnecting twin rooms.</p>
<p>Children under 13 years must be in the same room as an adult. Rooms are allocated according to party size.</p>
<p>Housekeeping is offered once mid-week.</p>
<p><strong>Room facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>All rooms have twin or double beds (please specify preference when booking)</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Ensuite shower room</li>
<li>WC (separate to shower)</li>
<li>Toiletries</li>
<li>Hairdryer (on request)</li>
<li>Beds are made on arrival</li>
<li>Towels and bed linen</li>
<li>House keeping is included (mid week clean)</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
